# _lightdash — zsh completion for **lightdash** — Lightdash CLI, the
#            developer tool for **dbt + Lightdash** —
#            Lightdash is the open-source business
#            intelligence / metrics layer that sits on top of dbt
#            (Data Build Tool), promoting it from a transformation-
#            only framework into a full BI platform: every Lightdash
#            "metric" / "dimension" / "explore" is sourced from a dbt
#            model's `schema.yml`, so the analytics-engineering
