#            checkout, deploy explores to a Lightdash server, create
#            ephemeral preview projects for a feature branch, run
#            saved charts headlessly, and authenticate against the
#            Lightdash API via OAuth 2.0 + OpenID Connect 1.0
#            (browser-based PKCE flow against the canonical Node
#            OIDC library `panva/node-openid-client`).  TS-Node=179
